# Contact form delivery — Formspree
# 1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io (connect it to your inbox)
# 2. Copy this file to `.env`, then paste your real endpoint below
# 3. Restart the dev server (Vite only reads .env at startup)
VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/your_form_id
